title: Should we add Bonus Bunny Pools?
body:
Hello everyone! As a special thank you for being part of the BUNNY family and sticking with us on our exciting journey, we would like to reward you all by offering new BUNNY and BUNNY-BNB special Bonus Pools that return additional BUNNY rewards!

By an earlier vote of the community, we reduced BUNNY emissions as of March 2. We propose to offer the Bunny Bonus pools for 4 weeks as a special token of our appreciation for your ongoing enthusiastic support! The Bunny Bonus will consist of new BUNNY minted to reward the community, calculated as a function of the reduction of emissions implemented 3/2 by popular vote.
